metadata.name: Возвышение #96
metadata.description:
Возвышение (Eng.: Elevation) is the next step of my study of Suprematism, textures and colours, partially inspired by Lazar Khidekel works. 
The work depicts the superiority of the simplest geometric forms and colours over everything else.

——————

Rendering takes around 20-30 seconds at 60 fps, might take longer on older devices.
Press [Arrow Up / Down] to increase / decrease drawing speed.
Press [1…6] to change an image resolution up to 10k.
Press [S] after the image is rendered to save it.

Created using p5.js.
License: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.

——————

hrunz. — Sep. 2022.

Generative animated drawing inspired by mindless doodling and low-res CAD graphics. Custom physics engine made with vanilla javascript. Colors quantized with GLSL. By @galoandstuff.

Screen size responsive.

metadata.name: Julia's Magical Bulbs - 3rd 4th 5th Powers #91
metadata.description:
Julia's Magical Bulbs are 3D dimensional fractals, based on the Julia Sets of the Mandelbulb fractal.  In this edition we explore the 3rd, 4th and 5th powers.

The token is interactive, use your mouse-wheel to zoom-in and see all the little details. You will find a menu in the lower-right corner which allows you to play with the iterations and camera position. You can also render high-resolution images here.

A little bit of magic happens when you select low iteration values, perhaps your token will even default to this.

Technical:

Not all browsers support multi-threaded modules, the fallback mode is quite slow. Try Chrome if your browser is not supported.

Calculated in full 64-bit on the CPU (not the GPU) for more accurate and detailed images.

metadata.name: A Bugged Forest #431
metadata.description:
A forest has stories to tell.
About times that were, about times that will be.
-
This project was minted in much unusual conditions. 
We gathered here, by 38 degrees heat. We belong to a crowd who loves stories, of civilisations at stake and deities, of afterlife and worship. We drank and hugged and chanted pagan hymns. We minted the Bugged Forest from our place on earth that we call Hell just for the fun of it. We are passionate, and loving, and angry and desperate. We, people of the soil, under a bugged sun.
-
This project is the long-form version of an algorithm that contains a bug. “The Bugged Tree”’s code was salvaged and stored and served as the core motivation and engine for an entire forest. Its concept is about releasing the control. I am a  byproduct of evolution, an iteration of that specie who wanted utter control, and which at some point, lost control over its own creation. As a generative artist, I chose to welcome the event of chance into my creative process. The symbolism in chance made me feel humble and free. Unwilling to make any change to a story that the Tree needed to tell me, as a listener, rather than a writer of my own idealised fantasies.
-
The iterations aren’t under control. They may be odd and off. We have to accept it. They are also plottable, press [s] in live mode to get a SVG. Attempt the plot at your own risk, as there’s a possibility for it to come near to impossibilities or cause paper or motor damage, and most certainly, a bugged drawing.
-
From Earth or from Hell, with love, yours truthfully, NFTBiker and zancan

metadata.name: JullyCar #197
metadata.description:
We all dream of having a car or we have

Some of us even talk to our car

And some of us see our car like a cartoon character.

This collection is not only an NFT but also a match
If you win one of the cups, in addition to a Super Rare edition, there are also prizes for the owners in the Primary market, which you can find on our Twitter ( @Morixels )

The JullyCar is unique random Generated 200 PFP NFTs. The number of Traits in this collection is 10 (168 layers) and it has the ability to make unique 124,582,993,920 NFTs.

To create balance, these NFTs are randomly minted, and this is a chance for everyone to get a rare version. So due to the low price of these NFTs, if the rare version did not belong to you, it is still possible for you to mint the new NFTs.

Because this is an NFT in PFP format, you can put it on your avatar on Twitter or Instagram.

This project is a collaboration project and it is a Benefit for the owners of the most Morixels to Collaborate with Morixels Designer.

You can read more information on Morixels website 👇

Website: https://morixels.com/

Twitter: @Morixels

by: @morteza_yousefy & @ardavan_
Made in 2022

metadata.name: LOST ANGELES - TheFEARZ #45
metadata.description:
Don´t have FOMO - FEARZ are here!

THE FEARZ UNIVERSE
A universe of over 10.000 NFTs - unique digital collectibles

There are 5 countries on the FEARZ Planet and one of them is LOST ANGELES.
In LOST ANGELES, everyone feels constantly alone. It is all far too big and unmanageable for any FEARZ. A constant feeling of being lost and uprooted repeats the experience of constant loss. When you leave home, you run the risk of never finding it again after a short time. It is like a huge labyrinth without an exit.

There will be 5 drops, one every two weeks for each country on the FEARZ planet.
(LOST ANGELES, PAINDAMIC, DEPRESSLAND, FRUSTRATIA, PANIC HILLS)

Whoever holds an NFT from each country on Saturday, 10th of Sep is qualified and receives a SPECIAL AIRDROP PACK!

metadata.name: fx(Restaurant) #34
metadata.description:
This is a text-based restaurant bill made up of fxhash's best-selling and selected artworks. Each item is randomly selected and priced according to the current floor and median prices.
The artworks are generally selected from famous and best-selling works.
This token is a kind of inside joke among fxhash collectors and artists and it was written in p5js and html, which means that the texts inside the artwork can be selected and copied.
